          <description><![CDATA[SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - Rookie Isaiah Collier drove for the go-ahead layup with 2 seconds left to lift the Utah Jazz to a 112-111 overtime victory over the Brooklyn Nets on Sunday night.]]></description>
